Package org.apache.kafka.connect.header

Interface Headers

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Header>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConnectHeaders
    public interface Headers
extends Iterable<Header>
    A mutable ordered collection of Header objects. Note that multiple headers may have the same key.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static interface  Headers.HeaderTransform
      A function to transform the supplied Header.
